      advice: "For Staff roles at Stripe: prepare an architecture presentation that you can defend under intense questioning. Every design choice should have a reason backed by data or first principles. Stripe values builders who can also communicate — if you can't write a clear design doc, you'll struggle at Staff regardless of your coding ability. Also: understand payments domain basics before interviewing. You don't need to be an expert, but knowing what 'idempotency key' means and why it matters shows you've done your homework.",
